{"word":"παιδοτρόφος","slug":"παιδοτρόφος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παιδοτρόφος</b></el> <el>(παιδο-τρόφος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:τρέφω'><el>τρέφω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>rearing boys</i>, <b><a href='S:Simonides Lyricus'>Simon.</a></b>: <el>παιδοτρόφος ἐλάα</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>as <a href='S:feminine'>fem.</a> <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a> <i>a mother</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}